window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Seth is being hunted by the Seven Seals.</p> <p>And he wants to go back to Earth. But he is not strong enough to do that, not when his life is constantly on the line from those who want him dead. However, when he is saved by a mysterious man by the name of Noah, he finds himself becoming strong enough to take back his life from those who had stolen it from him.</p> <p>Check out the action-packed sequel to Seth the Abyssal Assassin!</p>"; 
